msgstr "Bantuan"

#: app/templates/help.html:7
msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli menyertakan instruksi bawaan di seluruh aplikasi untuk membantu Anda "
"mengonfigurasi dan mengelola pengaturan Anda."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Halaman ini memberikan gambaran umum tentang fitur utama dan tautan langsung"
" ke tempat fitur tersebut dapat dikelola."

